{"tid":2412950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 曼聯明叔真係好鐘意自打嘴巴","createTime":"2021-02-18T10:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T10:19:54.000Z","uid":42246,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9c1d1ac724dd80a8327bc9d3ed4be6bf0587a5","tid":2412950,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"足球熱話｜曼聯名宿堅尼自打嘴巴玩IG　貼文反高潮兩日獲百萬追蹤 <br />\n<br />\nHK01<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n球員時代已是話題人物的曼聯名宿堅尼，近日連開設Instagram個人帳戶都成為足球界焦點，這位昔日中場悍將在情人節出Post，引來球迷激烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">一代曼聯鐵血隊長堅尼近年轉任評述員，在電視直播間不時批評保羅普巴等「紅魔」球員因沉迷社交網站而分心。不過這位曼聯名宿日前「自打嘴巴」，竟然在Instagram上開設個人帳户。</span><br />\n<br />\n堅尼的IG「惡搞」味甚濃，他以自己小時候的可愛照片做頭像，跟場上兇狠的他形成強烈對比。而他的第一個貼文便上載了自己跟愛犬的合照，並寫道：「人類最好的朋友」，盡顯男人的浪漫。<br />\n<br />\n這位前紅魔中場昨日情人節再「出招」，幽大家一默。他呼籲大家在情人節要向身邊人展示愛意，不過配圖卻令人意想不到：一張昔日他效力諾定咸森林時，跟韋斯咸球員史杜亞沙特（Stuart Slater）及比索（Ian Bishop）打架叉頸的相片，或者堅尼想說的是「打者愛也」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這個貼文除了引來網民紛紛讚好，同屬「講波佬」的加歷查亦有留言，以4個「笑到喊」的表情符號回應；而阿仙奴名宿伊恩胡禮就讚堅尼出post「有一手」，並笑指對方「好難捉摸」<br />\n<br />\n堅尼「加盟」IG成為體壇熱話，雖然他未有「追蹤」任何人，但開戶短短兩日就已獲過百萬人「追蹤」。<br />\n<br />\n「追蹤者」除萬人迷碧咸等外國球星，香港首席桌球手傅家俊、香港羽毛球「一哥」伍家朗及港超理文中場顏樂楓等本地運動員也不例外<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼聯明叔就是這樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3f6dcf2ab73304fdc44acf50e403dda5b3ef2e","tid":2412950,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823642fa71bdee3c01e7b2273b06b15e70b26301","tid":2412950,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"留名觀戰"},{"pid":"75b7feed52e5886ee90701547175e9259ea0f35d","tid":2412950,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"823642fa71bdee3c01e7b2273b06b15e70b26301","tid":2412950,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"留名觀戰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"條友又要自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0535afa0614b736bf71c41832b36dec9c15ca4","tid":2412950,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"推到明叔駁嘴"},{"pid":"e6e3f5b2b56264eced0ed45700dcf6ee1db8b18f","tid":2412950,"uid":38189,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5a0535afa0614b736bf71c41832b36dec9c15ca4","tid":2412950,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"推到明叔駁嘴"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"明叔笠左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df85b41479fb95a7ef5c35706eed8a66b3b383e6","tid":2412950,"uid":52571,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e6e3f5b2b56264eced0ed45700dcf6ee1db8b18f","tid":2412950,"uid":38189,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5a0535afa0614b736bf71c41832b36dec9c15ca4","tid":2412950,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"推到明叔駁嘴"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"明叔笠左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"應該組織緊 叔哥少少漏口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f79f18a3d4097c321d7f243c6f095a3b7711319","tid":2412950,"uid":3747,